name: 2001 loire Nantes wood digital photo move
description:
When I studied Ecole des beaux art de Nantes France, there are studio in a town(Rue des Olivette) . I went to the studio from my small apartment in front of cathedral ( 5,place Deumoustier) . a top floor like a Gibri movie Kiki. 


I went to studio by kickboard with black cap. 

In Saturday there is a market by agriculture.  have some oyster.  Because Nantes is riverside city from 30 km by the Atlantic Ocean. 



I ate oyster with baguette. So this a sculpture when I was a stay in France at that time. I bring this sculpture into the nature and put on the title where was taking photography with Contax 35mm Film camera. 



When you are alone in a different country, look back to own Spirit. If you put your body on a different country, you will find originality reflecting from the people and environment. a different air, different water and different sky. This is my sculpture.  She can live on eternity in the NFT Crypto world. 2021 July 18. Tokyo Hideki.
